Summary: 4 Amber Lights in the shape of Boomerang
divs: Sighting DetailsI just pushed out the trash bins at its curve side for tomorrow pickup and saw a 4-amber lights in the shape of a boomrang that it flew silently over head in the direction of North to South towards the Disneyland, Anaheim about 8:55PM. The event happened so fast that I've been stunned to see it passing by and not enough time to take a picture even though my digital camera were inside and on my desk. My guess its altitude is about the same as of a small Cessna-typed plane.
